=== 票房 ===
北美方面，首周末取得4040万美元成为周末冠军，并创造了史上一月份第二高的首映成绩，仅次于2014年黑人喜剧片《[[佐州自救兄弟|佐州自救兄弟]]》4150万美元的历史记录。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.mtime.com/2015/01/12/1538228.html |title=《飓风营救3》北美首周登顶 |access-date=2015-01-12 |archive-date=2019-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213005534/http://news.mtime.com/2015/01/12/1538228.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>中国大陆首周三天取得1.095亿人民币列第三位，次周收8200万蝉联第三，最终成绩为2.066亿。

香港方面，首周四天收获941万港币居冠。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.1905.com/news/20150108/844099.shtml |title=香港票房：《飓风营救3》登顶 《博物馆3》第二 |access-date=2015-01-08 |archive-date=2019-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212131448/http://www.1905.com/news/20150108/844099.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>次周收入560万蝉联冠军。

台灣方面，首週三天票房為新台幣6000萬元<ref>{{cite news |title=周末全台票房排行榜 |url=https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20150116/36330177 |work=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] |date=2015-01-16 |accessdate=2019-02-12 |archive-date=2018-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180203064113/https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20150116/36330177/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；次週票房累計至新台幣1.2億元<ref>{{cite news |title=周末全台票房排行榜 |url=https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20150123/36344981 |work=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] |date=2015-01-23 |accessdate=2019-02-12 |archive-date=2018-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180202193241/https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20150123/36344981 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；第三週票房累計至新台幣1.55億元<ref>{{cite news |title=周末全台票房排行榜 |url=https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20150130/36359499 |work=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] |date=2015-01-30 |accessdate=2019-02-12 |archive-date=2018-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180202191648/https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20150130/36359499 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；第四週票房累計至新台幣1.7億元<ref>{{cite news |title=周末全台票房排行榜 |url=https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20150206/36373173 |work=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] |date=2015-02-06 |accessdate=2019-02-12 |archive-date=2018-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180202191635/https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20150206/36373173 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；最終全台票房為新台幣1.77億元<ref>{{cite web|author1=項貽斐|title=上半年全台總票房 12大片進帳破億|url=http://udn.com/news/story/7262/1053350|work=[[聯合報|聯合報]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150822000154/http://udn.com/news/story/7262/1053350|archivedate=2015-08-22|date=2015-07-14|accessdate=2019-02-12}}</ref>。

